  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the chopped onion and saut\u00157 until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "add the tandoor spice blend and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "add the chopped parsley and cilantro, and cook for an additional 1 minute, until wilted.",
    "add the cooked pappardelle pasta to the skillet, and toss to combine with the onion and spice mixture.",
    "season with salt, black pepper, and crushed red pepper flakes, to taste.",
    "top the pasta with crispy tandoor chickpeas and chopped almonds.",
    "garnish with additional parsley and cilantro, if desired."
